X
(C_p(X), +)
x\in X
(f+g)(x)=f(x)+g(x)
+:C_p(X)\times C_p(X)\to C_p(X):(f,g)\mapsto f+g
C_p(X)
f
\{O(f, x_1,\ldots, x_n, \epsilon) : n \in\Bbb N, x_1,\ldots, x_n \in X,\epsilon > 0\}\;,
O(f, x_1,\ldots, x_n,\epsilon) =\{g \in C_p(X) : \vert g(x_i)- f(x_i) \vert<\epsilon \; \text{for all }i\leq n\}
